text: As a quick refresher, Unglert and Lombard’s romance on Bachelor In Paradise effervesced, but ended up being part of a never-ending love triangle with Kristina Schulman. The juggling act got the best of him and ultimately all of the relationships imploded (this is reality TV after all). Unglert also made it to Lindsay's final four during her season of The Bachelorette, before he was out of the running to become America's next top husband.
